Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:15.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And now for the final exercise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:17.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Swing your arms out wide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:21.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,then cross them in front of you\Nas you take slow, deep breaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In... And out...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:25.67,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I came to check on you since \Nbreak time's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:27.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In... And out...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:27.17,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Things are quite lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:30.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:33.22,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:36.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:37.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:42.17,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so much younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:51.87,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone has touched me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:52.78,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Barusu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:55.10,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of game is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:57.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Radio calisthenics.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:01:00.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I think the fact that everyone, \Nyoung and old, can enjoy it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:03.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,is the secret to its many long years of success!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.24,0:01:04.75,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:06.00,Default,Mildo,0000,0000,0000,,Ram-chi, that was cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:07.54,Default,Dyne,0000,0000,0000,,Ram-chi, that was mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:09.20,Default,Lucas,0000,0000,0000,,Ram-chi, you're scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:13.83,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Did you teach these children to call me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.83,0:01:15.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:18.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to spread some friendliness around?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:22.26,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind, but what about Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:23.78,Default,Mildo,0000,0000,0000,,Rem-rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:24.90,Default,Dyne,0000,0000,0000,,Rem-rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:26.03,Default,Lucas,0000,0000,0000,,Rem-rin-rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:31.86,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,And? Did you enjoy the village \Ntrip you wanted so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.26,0:01:34.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to worry about there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:38.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,When Muraosa patted my shoulder at \Nthe end, my trip was complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:42.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna say something, out with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:44.75,Default,Maylie,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:46.12,Default,Maylie,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:53.78,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Have your way a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.34,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.77,0:01:58.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I owe you both, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:12.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, there was an event like this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.97,0:02:16.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And this still happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.62,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,She's usually so tame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:20.24,Default,Mildo,0000,0000,0000,,She only gets mad at Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:22.79,Default,Lucas,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do to her, Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:25.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'd like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:29.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If it's happened three times, \NI guess we're just incompatible...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:30.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:32.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:37.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's the sensation I've longed to feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:40.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! For a stray, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:43.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you have a bald spot on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A scar? What did you walk int—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:47.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:50.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You even bit me in nearly the same spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:52.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a time traveler?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:55.78,Default,Lucas,0000,0000,0000,,You got carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:57.83,Default,Mildo,0000,0000,0000,,It's what you get for touching her so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:02:59.57,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,She is a girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:02.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's quite the problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:04.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Also, no one's worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I made it... I made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:12.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, me! Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.83,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.51,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:21.44,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see the three of you are together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:23.98,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,That will save me some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.14,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Roswaal-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:27.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Formal clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:30.04,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Well spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:34.32,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seeing someone who's a hassle \Nto deal with in normal attire,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:37.68,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,so I had no choice but to wear dress clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:38.99,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,A visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:39.86,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,You're going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:43.28,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Ram is correct. I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:47.52,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,I received a message that \Nwas a tad troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:49.20,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm off to make the rounds outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:53.64,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,I do not expect to be home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:56.24,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ram and Rem, take care of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:58.13,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. As you command.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:59.92,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Even if it costs our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:04.50,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Roswaal didn't leave the mansion before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:08.34,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also be counting on you, Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:12.10,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of Emilia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:15.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you can definitely count on me for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:18.72,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Then, look after things while I'm away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:21.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,H-He can fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:28.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.04,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The difference in circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:36.54,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,must have been triggered \Nby my visit to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:40.50,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That means my strategy of acting \Nas a decoy is working as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.97,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why I'm here for my \Nlong-awaited Beako time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.90,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Your face looks quite different \Nthan it did half a day ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:51.22,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,You've been busy, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:54.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to take it easy for a change, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:56.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But there's something I want \Nyou to check out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:02.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've been cursed. \NCould you find out for sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:04.48,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:07.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've been cursed. \NCould you find out for sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:11.07,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,No one asked you to repeat yourself, I suppose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:14.63,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,It's only been half a day since \NI told you about shamans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:15.79,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,You're far too impressionabl—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:19.32,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Traces of a curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:21.30,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,You really have been cursed, I suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:25.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So the shaman was one \Nof the villagers, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:27.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell what kind of curse it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:31.58,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say just from looking at the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.98,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,But as I told you, once it's activated,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.35,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,chances are you'll die, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:42.69,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to be afraid of dying at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:46.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm insanely scared of dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:50.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing in the world that \Nscares me more than dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:53.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wish people who say "I'd rather die" \Nwould actually die before they say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:57.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, this time, I'll find a way out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:00.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,of this fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:03.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so get rid of this curse for me, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:05.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:08.83,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I have to save your life, I suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:11.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I expected an unlovable response like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:14.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,so I came prepared to convince you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:17.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, Puck is bound to be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:18.95,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:23.02,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Bubby wouldn't be all that disturbed if you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to die, Emilia would \Nbe at least a little shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:30.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,When Emilia feels shock, \NPuck takes damage, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:34.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And if you could have stopped it,\Nbut didn't, what would he think of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:39.08,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go along with your smooth \Ntalk this time, I suppose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:42.54,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,But after this, I'll have nothing \Nmore to do with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:46.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But when I'm in trouble, \NI'll always come to ask for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:53.20,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy the spell used in \Nthe curse now, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:57.94,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,The spell is burned into you on the \Nspot that the shaman touched,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:06:59.10,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,so that's our reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:02.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I prepared for this. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.70,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The young men's leader with the crew cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:07.24,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The old lady who felt so much younger \Nthat she patted my butt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:09.22,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And Muraosa, the fake village head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:12.28,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I made sure all the suspects \Ntouched different parts of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:26.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A black mist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.44,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,How abhorrent, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:34.72,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,All done. You'll be fine now, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:39.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So the place that the black mist came from
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is where the shaman touched me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Could that puppy actually be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:51.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:56.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,They just keep messing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:07:59.79,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,The village? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:05.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Beatrice said the one who gave me this \Nwound is responsible for cursing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:08.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It was the dog that the kids were playing with!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:13.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That dog-looking thing cursed everyone it bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:15.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I do nothing, they'll be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:19.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't trust me, you can come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:22.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't leave Emilia alone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:24.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Only one of you can come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.54,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You're making up your own rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:29.55,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,And if we are to obey Roswaal-sama's orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:32.15,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,there is no reason for either \Nof us to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:38.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But was that the only order Roswaal gave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.21,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, Barusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll allow you to act on your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:44.80,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.45,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Rem will accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I wanted to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:51.29,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, that's my decision, so please go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:54.97,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I'll confirm with Beatrice-sama \Nand protect Emilia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.98,Default,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep an eye on that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:59.90,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, you shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.47,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, are you going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:05.50,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I heard loud voices, so I came down \Nto see what was going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:06.40,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:09.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Something might {\i1}be{\i0} happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:10.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:13.64,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're going to do \Nsomething dangerous again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:17.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We were just wrapping up a dispute \Non that particular topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:19.87,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop you, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:22.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.91,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, if you do, it'd be a \Nhindrance in several ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:30.17,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:32.26,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:35.76,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably no use telling you not\Nto be rash or reckless, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:38.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on what happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:41.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's not like I want to do any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:46.94,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,May the blessing of the spirits be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:48.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:54.19,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It's a prayer to send you off. \NIt means "come back safely."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:57.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, Emilia-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:00.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:01.87,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:17.72,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:21.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... Several of the village \Nchildren have gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.68,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All the adults are looking for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Was I too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:31.45,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:47.63,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,The barrier is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:50.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What happens when the barrier's broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:53.13,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Mabeasts can cross the boundary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Mabeasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:57.71,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Mabeasts are creatures of the witch's creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.63,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,They're enemies of humanity \Nthat have magic powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:03.10,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,They live gregariously in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Gregariously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:08.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You mean tons more dogs \Nlike that one are out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:14.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:16.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Tell everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:16.94,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:22.31,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:24.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go save those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:27.28,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You can't make that decision on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:29.94,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,With Roswaal-sama away from home,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:34.06,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,can you be sure that this isn't a ruse to \Ndivert attention from the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:38.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore kids who are in trouble right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,go back to the mansion, and tighten security?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:43.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't care when all the \Nvillagers are dead tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:45.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:50.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, let's go. We're the only ones\Nwho can do something about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.90,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Why go so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:56.16,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Why should this village matter to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:57.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Petra...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:01.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,When she grows up, she wants to \Nmake clothes in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.11,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:06.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Lucas wants to succeed the \Nvillage's best woodcutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:10.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Mildo wants to make a crown \Nfrom the flowers in the fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and give it to his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:16.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Meina is going to have a baby sister soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:21.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And the brothers, Dyne and Cain, are \Nalways fighting over who'll marry Petra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:28.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,They do matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:30.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I know their names, their faces,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and what they want to do in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:37.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And I promised them we'd do radio \Ncalisthenics again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:41.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I keep my promises, and I make \Nsure others keep theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:47.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do radio calisthenics \Nwith those kids again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:49.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.98,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:13:00.09,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,My orders were to keep an eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:02.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure I don't do anything shady!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:08.72,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.03,0:13:16.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Rem-san, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.17,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It's for protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:19.60,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It's for protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:34.00,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,We're close. I smell something alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:35.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.42,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure, but it doesn't smell like animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:51.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's the kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:56.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,They're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:00.35,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're still breathing now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they are very weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:02.82,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,If left alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Weak... The curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And we finally found them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, can't you undo it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:14.56,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I lack the skill for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:17.12,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,If only my sister were here to see them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:21.10,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,But I will cast a healing spell to comfort them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:23.11,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,When they're calm, we'll carry them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:27.07,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:29.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I'm so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep watch—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.14,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:34.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake, Petra?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right, good. You're a tough girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:38.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:41.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you back home, where you \Ncan say goodbye to the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just rest for—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.52,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,One is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:47.52,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,still... in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what'd you say? Petra!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:57.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, she's right. I don't \Nsee the little girl with the braid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:15:00.80,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please, wait! It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:03.28,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,And if the mabeasts took her, it's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:06.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I get what you're saying! I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:07.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But, Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:10.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Petra says another girl was taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:16.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She showed concern for her friend\Nbefore asking for my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:19.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She put her friend before herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:24.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to respect Petra's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:27.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you take something on, you should \Nmake the effort to take it all on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.15,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,If you get too greedy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:32.49,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,you might take on more \Nthan you can carry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:36.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're with me, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.54,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,What does that have to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:42.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids need you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,When the villagers show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:46.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,leave the kids with them and follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:52.06,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know the threat our opponent \Npresents, or when the villagers will arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:55.60,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,And at worst, there is a chance \NI won't be able to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:58.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine. You won't lose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.50,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:04.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even if no one else does, \Nyou can pick up my scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:07.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The foul odor that hangs on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of the witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:10.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:13.74,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun, how much do you know about...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:17.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No idea... There's a ton I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:20.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So much that no matter how \Nmany times I start over,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find the answer I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:27.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just like there are things you want to ask me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:31.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,there are tons of things I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So when this is all taken care of, let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:36.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Until our voices are hoarse! Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:45.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to act in a way \Nthat makes you trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:48.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make that promise right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:53.47,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. The promise is made.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:56.66,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I will ask you many questions, so be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:16:58.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:01.33,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Once the villagers come for \Nthe kids, I'll come join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:04.09,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:08.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I'm fanatical like a demon today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.50,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Fanatical... like a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:12.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's the demon version of divine possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:15.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's my favorite phrase lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:18.01,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:29.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If the one that cursed those kids \Nreally was that dog from today,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:32.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way I can lose, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:35.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I smell animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:47.87,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.36,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia wouldn't hesitate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:05.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:21.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is not what we discussed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:23.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so huge?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:28.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And was it waiting for me to come for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:31.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nowhere to run...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:37.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! If you wanna fight, bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:50.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:52.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:56.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You just bit me, didn't you, you moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.44,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I won...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:26.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna fight, bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:44.34,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,The children have been safely \Nreturned to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:46.99,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for buying time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, watch ou—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.02,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:57.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:20:00.44,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if that's a nice thing \Nto say to a girl, Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:04.65,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I have no other words to describe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:06.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:13.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So, Rem, would you be able to take them \Nall out in one shot, by chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:16.40,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,We are outnumbered. With this \Nmany, our situation is dire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:19.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In that case... There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:22.22,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, I don't know the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.52,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:47.79,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Once we cross the barrier, the battle will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:49.34,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Run toward the village bonfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:50.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:03.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, I see light!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:05.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost to the barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:24.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:42.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.01,0:22:20.61,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Mabeast! Mabeast! Mabeast! Mabeast!
